game.name: Disney Princess Design
game.description:
The extremely beautiful princess Cinderella has already won the crown of being the best fashion stylist in the whole fairytale world. Today the Grand Disney Ball has been organized in the evening and she was selected as the chief designer of the event. So, this Disney princess now needs your help to design outstanding gowns. Would you help her out during this difficult task? Join the Disney Princess Design game and be prepared to help her prepare perfect dresses for all the princesses!

She has to prepare gorgeous ball gowns for Elsa, Rapunzel, Belle and other popular princesses. Use your fashion advice to help the princess complete the task successfully in this brand new dressing game for girls! Firstly, choose a game mode between freestyle and challenge mode. In challenge mode, you will have a full freedom to select a shape and color for top and bottom. Then give her a lovely hairstyle, and add some other accessories like a pair of hand gloves, and matching jewelry items.

In the freestyle mode, you can also give a shape and color for the gown. You can also add some other useful items to the top and bottom parts of the gown. Hurry up, ladies! Other princesses are also waiting for their turn. Do fast and design a party-looking gown for all the girls in this html5 princess dress-up game! All the best to create the perfect party dresses in our other popular titles from the huge category of girls games! Enjoy a lot every day at our free game website, no download required!
